<div><head>喻歸西河記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.2">姑臧匈奴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.3">故蓋臧城也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.4">城不方有頭尾雨翅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.5">名蓋鳥城。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.6">《初學記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.7">涼州辠人於市將刑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.8">忽有一白雄雞飛於人邊請命，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.9">引頸長鳴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.10">伏地向吏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.11">驅之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.12">去，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.13">輒來。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.14">刺史張義色其坐。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-1a.15">《藝文類聚》、《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.2">張駿立謙光殿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.3">成後池水中有五龍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.4">晝日見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.5">移時乃滅。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.6">水通變綠色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.7">駿因作鑄銅龍以厭之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.8">後卒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.9">不勝此殿。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-2a.10">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.2">西河無蠶桑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.3">婦女著碧纈裙，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.4">加細布裳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.5">著纈襦襖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.6">以外國五色錦為袴褶。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.7">《北堂書鈔》、《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.8">貸我東墻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.9">償我白梁。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-3a.10">《漢書》注、《史記索隱》、《齊民要術》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.2">趙倫妻死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.3">遺雪竹搔頭階下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.4">不數日化為楊梅𠌶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.5">朵如撒時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.6">人異之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.7">《太平御覽》引《姑臧記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.8">錢芸士好讀《離騷》，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.9">手不暇揭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.10">忘去肉味，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.11">半月如齋。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1316_CHANT_001-4a.12">《太平御覽》引《姑臧記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
